<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>深淵之境 — 深海探索</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@300;400;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --abyss: #030810;
      --deep: #050d1a;
      --mid: #0a1e3d;
      --surface: #0e2f5c;
      --glow: #00c8f0;
      --glow-dim: #0098b8;
      --ghost: #d0eaf5;
      --mist: #7ab8d0;
      --bio: #00ffe0;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--abyss);
      color: var(--ghost);
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* ── Particle canvas ── */
    #particles {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    section, header, footer { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1.25rem 4rem;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(3,8,16,0.9) 0%, transparent 100%);
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--glow);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--mist);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--glow); }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-depth-label {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--glow);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s 0.3s forwards;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: var(--ghost);
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s 0.6s forwards;
    }

    .hero h1 span {
      color: var(--glow);
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--mist);
      line-height: 1.8;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s 0.9s forwards;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s 1.2s forwards;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 0.7rem 2rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--glow);
      color: var(--abyss);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--bio);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(0,200,240,0.4);
    }

    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--glow);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,200,240,0.4);
    }

    .btn-outline:hover {
      border-color: var(--glow);
      box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(0,200,240,0.2);
    }

    .scroll-hint {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 2rem;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s 2s forwards;
    }

    .scroll-hint span {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--mist);
    }

    .scroll-line {
      width: 1px;
      height: 50px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--glow), transparent);
      animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    /* ── JELLYFISH (signature element) ── */
    .jellyfish-wrap {
      position: absolute;
      right: 8%;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 200px;
      height: 260px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s 1.5s forwards;
    }

    .jelly-body {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 120px;
      height: 80px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 40% 30%, rgba(0,255,224,0.18) 0%, rgba(0,200,240,0.08) 60%, transparent 100%);
      border-radius: 60% 60% 40% 40% / 80% 80% 20% 20%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,200,240,0.3);
      animation: jellyPulse 4s ease-in-out infinite, jellyFloat 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .jelly-inner {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 60px;
      height: 30px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(0,255,224,0.12) 0%, transparent 100%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,224,0.15);
    }

    .jelly-tentacle {
      position: absolute;
      top: 75px;
      width: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,200,240,0.4), transparent);
      animation: tentacleWave 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      transform-origin: top;
      border-radius: 1px;
    }

    .jelly-tentacle:nth-child(1) { left: 30%; height: 80px; animation-delay: 0s; }
    .jelly-tentacle:nth-child(2) { left: 38%; height: 110px; animation-delay: 0.3s; }
    .jelly-tentacle:nth-child(3) { left: 46%; height: 95px; animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .jelly-tentacle:nth-child(4) { left: 54%; height: 120px; animation-delay: 0.5s; }
    .jelly-tentacle:nth-child(5) { left: 62%; height: 85px; animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .jelly-tentacle:nth-child(6) { left: 70%; height: 100px; animation-delay: 0.4s; }

    /* ── STATS BAND ── */
    .stats {
      padding: 5rem 4rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 2px;
      background: rgba(14,47,92,0.2);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,200,240,0.08);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,200,240,0.08);
    }

    .stat-item {
      padding: 2rem 3rem;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    .stat-item::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      top: 20%;
      height: 60%;
      width: 1px;
      background: rgba(0,200,240,0.1);
    }

    .stat-item:last-child::after { display: none; }

    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--glow);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .stat-unit {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--mist);
      margin-left: 2px;
    }

    .stat-label {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--mist);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── ZONES SECTION ── */
    .zones {
      padding: 8rem 4rem;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--glow);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
      color: var(--ghost);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .section-desc {
      max-width: 500px;
      color: var(--mist);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .zones-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1px;
      background: rgba(0,200,240,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,200,240,0.06);
    }

    .zone-card {
      padding: 3rem;
      background: rgba(5,13,26,0.9);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: background 0.4s;
    }

    .zone-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 3px;
      height: 0;
      background: var(--glow);
      transition: height 0.4s ease;
    }

    .zone-card:hover::before { height: 100%; }
    .zone-card:hover { background: rgba(10,30,61,0.9); }

    .zone-depth {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--glow-dim);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .zone-name {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--ghost);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .zone-desc {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--mist);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .zone-icon {
      position: absolute;
      right: 2rem;
      bottom: 2rem;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      opacity: 0.12;
    }

    /* ── CREATURES ── */
    .creatures {
      padding: 8rem 4rem;
      background: rgba(10,30,61,0.3);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .creatures-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .creatures-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .creature-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .creature-card {
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,200,240,0.1);
      border-radius: 2px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }

    .creature-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0,200,240,0.35);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .creature-glow {
      position: absolute;
      top: -30px;
      right: -30px;
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,200,240,0.07), transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .creature-emoji {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .creature-name {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--ghost);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .creature-latin {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--glow-dim);
      font-style: italic;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .creature-desc {
      font-size: 0.83rem;
      color: var(--mist);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── DIVE BAR ── */
    .dive-bar {
      padding: 7rem 4rem;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .depth-meter {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      position: relative;
    }

    .depth-track {
      height: 3px;
      background: rgba(0,200,240,0.12);
      border-radius: 2px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .depth-fill {
      height: 100%;
      width: 0%;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--glow-dim), var(--bio));
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: width 2s ease;
    }

    .depth-labels {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .depth-labels span {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      color: var(--mist);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .depth-readout {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--glow);
      margin-top: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .depth-readout span {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--mist);
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      padding: 3rem 4rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,200,240,0.06);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--glow);
    }

    .footer-copy {
      font-size: 0.73rem;
      color: rgba(122,184,208,0.4);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to   { opacity: 1; }
    }

    @keyframes jellyFloat {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0px); }
      50%       { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-20px); }
    }

    @keyframes jellyPulse {
      0%, 100% { border-radius: 60% 60% 40% 40% / 80% 80% 20% 20%; }
      50%       { border-radius: 55% 55% 45% 45% / 70% 70% 30% 30%; }
    }

    @keyframes tentacleWave {
      0%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg) scaleX(1); }
      25%       { transform: rotate(8deg) scaleX(1.3); }
      75%       { transform: rotate(-8deg) scaleX(0.8); }
    }

    @keyframes scrollPulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; }
      50%       { opacity: 1; }
    }

    @keyframes bubbleRise {
      0%   { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); opacity: 0.6; }
      100% { transform: translateY(-100vh) scale(1.3); opacity: 0; }
    }

    /* ── SCROLL REVEAL ── */
    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
    }

    .reveal.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero { padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
      .jellyfish-wrap { display: none; }
      .stats { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
      .zones { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
      .zones-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .creatures { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
      .creature-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .creatures-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; }
      .dive-bar { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>

  </head>

  <body>

    <canvas id="particles"></canvas>

    <!-- NAV -->
    <nav>
      <a href="#" class="nav-logo">深淵之境</a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#zones">深海區域</a></li>
        <li><a href="#creatures">深淵生物</a></li>
        <li><a href="#dive">潛入深處</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <header class="hero">
      <p class="hero-depth-label">探索深度 · 11,000 米以下</p>
      <h1>黑暗之下<span>生命依然存在</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        在陽光無法抵達的地方，壓力足以壓碎鋼鐵，溫度接近冰點——卻有著最奇異的生命正在悄然繁盛。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#zones" class="btn btn-primary">開始探索</a>
        <a href="#creatures" class="btn btn-outline">深淵生物</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Jellyfish -->
      <div class="jellyfish-wrap">
        <div class="jelly-body">
          <div class="jelly-inner"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="jelly-tentacle"></div>
        <div class="jelly-tentacle"></div>
        <div class="jelly-tentacle"></div>
        <div class="jelly-tentacle"></div>
        <div class="jelly-tentacle"></div>
        <div class="jelly-tentacle"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="scroll-hint">
        <!-- <span>向下潛行</span> -->
        <div class="scroll-line"></div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- STATS -->
    <section class="stats">
      <div class="stat-item reveal">
        <div class="stat-num">11<span class="stat-unit">km</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">馬里亞納海溝最深處</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item reveal">
        <div class="stat-num">1,100<span class="stat-unit">atm</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">最深處水壓</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item reveal">
        <div class="stat-num">80<span class="stat-unit">%</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">海洋仍未被探索</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item reveal">
        <div class="stat-num">2°<span class="stat-unit">C</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">深海平均水溫</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ZONES -->
    <section class="zones" id="zones">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">深海分層</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">從陽光到永夜<br>每層都是新世界</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">
          海洋依光線滲透深度劃分為截然不同的生態區，越往下越陌生，越往下越不可思議。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="zones-grid reveal">
        <div class="zone-card">
          <div class="zone-depth">0 — 200 m</div>
          <div class="zone-name">透光層</div>
          <div class="zone-desc">陽光穿透，光合作用發生於此，是海洋食物鏈的能量起點。珊瑚礁、鯊魚、鮪魚都生活在這個明亮的世界。</div>
          <div class="zone-icon">☀️</div>
        </div>
        <div class="zone-card">
          <div class="zone-depth">200 — 1,000 m</div>
          <div class="zone-name">微光層</div>
          <div class="zone-desc">光線在這裡逐漸消逝。許多生物在此進行晝夜垂直遷徙，夜晚上升覓食，白天沉入暗處躲避掠食者。</div>
          <div class="zone-icon">🌑</div>
        </div>
        <div class="zone-card">
          <div class="zone-depth">1,000 — 4,000 m</div>
          <div class="zone-name">漸深層</div>
          <div class="zone-desc">全然黑暗，壓力極高。生物演化出生物發光能力，用光來誘捕獵物、辨識同類，或迷惑天敵。</div>
          <div class="zone-icon">✨</div>
        </div>
        <div class="zone-card">
          <div class="zone-depth">4,000 m 以下</div>
          <div class="zone-name">深淵層</div>
          <div class="zone-desc">地球上最孤寂的環境。食物靠「海雪」從上層緩緩沉降，這裡的生物緩慢、古老、近乎透明，等待宇宙般漫長。</div>
          <div class="zone-icon">❄️</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CREATURES -->
    <section class="creatures" id="creatures">
      <div class="creatures-inner">
        <div class="creatures-header">
          <div class="reveal">
            <p class="section-eyebrow">深淵居民</p>
            <h2 class="section-title">來自黑暗的<br>進化奇蹟</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="section-desc reveal" style="margin-bottom:0; text-align:right;">
            黑暗、寒冷、高壓——這些對生命的極限挑戰，<br>造就了地球上最獨特的演化路徑。
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="creature-cards">
          <div class="creature-card reveal">
            <div class="creature-glow"></div>
            <span class="creature-emoji">🐟</span>
            <div class="creature-name">鮟鱇魚</div>
            <div class="creature-latin">Lophiiformes</div>
            <div class="creature-desc">頭頂懸掛著會發光的「誘餌」，靜靜等待獵物靠近。雄魚極小，終身附著在雌魚身上共生，是自然界最極端的性別差異之一。</div>
          </div>
          <div class="creature-card reveal">
            <div class="creature-glow"></div>
            <span class="creature-emoji">🦑</span>
            <div class="creature-name">大王烏賊</div>
            <div class="creature-latin">Architeuthis dux</div>
            <div class="creature-desc">地球上最大的無脊椎動物，眼睛如足球般大，是自然界中最大的眼睛。牠們在深海與抹香鯨進行史詩般的搏鬥。</div>
          </div>
          <div class="creature-card reveal">
            <div class="creature-glow"></div>
            <span class="creature-emoji">🌊</span>
            <div class="creature-name">獅子魚</div>
            <div class="creature-latin">Pseudoliparis belyaevi</div>
            <div class="creature-desc">在馬里亞納海溝 8,336 公尺深處被發現，打破了脊椎動物深度紀錄。牠們的細胞含有特殊化合物，使蛋白質在極端壓力下依然正常運作。</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- DIVE DEPTH METER -->
    <section class="dive-bar" id="dive">
      <p class="section-eyebrow reveal">互動體驗</p>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">你願意潛到多深？</h2>
      <p class="section-desc reveal" style="margin: 0 auto 0; text-align: center;">
        拖動滑桿，感受深度與壓力的關係
      </p>

      <div class="depth-meter reveal">
        <input type="range" id="depthSlider" min="0" max="11000" value="0"
          style="width:100%; margin-top: 2rem;" >
          <!-- oninput="updateDepth(this.value)" -->
        <div class="depth-track" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          <div class="depth-fill" id="depthFill"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="depth-labels">
          <span>海面</span>
          <span>200m 微光層</span>
          <span>4000m 深淵</span>
          <span>11km 最深</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="depth-readout reveal" id="depthReadout">
        0 <span>公尺</span>
      </div>
      <p id="depthContext" style="color: var(--mist); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; min-height: 1.5rem; transition: opacity 0.3s;"></p>
    </section>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer>
      <div class="footer-logo">深淵之境</div>
      <div class="footer-copy">探索未知 · 敬畏自然 · 保護海洋</div>
    </footer>

    <script src="../scripts/script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>